Challenges/Approach:
Features like lags, most common, count, descriptive outcome of lag features along with time/date based, other intuitive features improved the score.
Encoding features like mean, count through time basedcross validation improved the score.
Different CV strategies like Kfold, Timeseries split were tried.
Dropping certain features at different combinations had some impact on the model results
In final model, Date based cross validation strategy has been used as Train/Test have different dates
